{
  "stem": "9168.6",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that's why we all congregated together.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I know that we, we talked about something that may have happened that day during the trial.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We also talked an awful lot about our lives in the countries where we came from, which was interesting.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean, we bonded with some of the British.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we talked about our lives elsewhere, before we ever got there, and things that happened, you know.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "What we were going to do when we returned, plans for the future, so--",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I was involved in-- I went in and out of, I think, certainly three of the trials subsequently.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But as opposed to the doctors' trial, which I reported from the beginning to the end with these other reporters, I went in and out on a daily assignment basis into these other three courtrooms.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I do not have the-- you know, a great deal of memory, or I have not retained the knowledge, too much, of what went on in those, those-- in that testimony.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But one was the IG Farben Industry trial, which was the United States of America versus Karl Krauch-- K-A-R-L K-R-A-U-C-H.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And another was the United States of America versus Alfried Krupp von Bohlen, von Bohlen, und Halbach, who Alfried Krupp was of the munitions family, and the son of the old Gustav, Krupp, who was initially indicted in the major Nazi trial by mistake.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was an 85-year-old man who had stroke.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so rather than substitute the son for him in that major trial, they tried him subsequently.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I know I was in another trial that involved the Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But I do not know which of those titles covered that trial.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] May of 1948.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
